\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</span><!-- Overwrite Story Content --><span>\n\n\t\t\t\t     \t  \t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span><span>\n\t\t\t\t\t  \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t            </span><span class=\"p-content\">\n\t            \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t\t      <style>span.p-content div[id^=\"div-gpt\"]{line-height:0;font-size:0}</style>\n\t\t\t\t    \t<div><span>\n\t\n\tShares of </span><a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/topic/bgr-energy-systems\" target=\"_blank\">BGR Energy Systems </a><span>have surged 18% to Rs 108 per share on the </span><a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/topic/bse\" target=\"_blank\">BSE </a><span>on back of heavy volumes after the company announced that it has secured two orders worth of Rs 4.31 billion from </span><a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/search?type=news&amp;q=nuclear+power+corporation+of+india\" target=\"_blank\">Nuclear Power Corporation of India </a><span>for </span><a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/search?type=news&amp;q=kudankulam+nuclear+power+projects\" target=\"_blank\">Kudankulam Nuclear Power projects </a><span>– 3 &amp; 4.</span><p>\n\tThe company bagged Rs 3.45 billion order for design &amp; detailed engineering, manufacture, procurement, supply, etc., of 400KV &amp; 230KV Switchyards and BoP electrical areas for <a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/search?type=news&amp;q=kudankulam+nuclear+power+projects\" target=\"_blank\">Kudankulam Nuclear Power projects </a>– 3 &amp; 4, <a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/topic/bgr-energy-systems\" target=\"_blank\">BGR Energy Systems </a>said in a press release.\n\n\n</p><span>\n</span><!-- INPAGE_BANNER --><p>\n\tThe second order worth of Rs 862 million for loading/unloading, transportation &amp; handling at site, storage, civil works, etc., of 400KV &amp; 230KV Switchyards and BoP electrical areas for <a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/search?type=news&amp;q=kudankulam+nuclear+power+projects\" target=\"_blank\">Kudankulam Nuclear Power projects </a>– 3 &amp; 4, it added.</p><p>\n\tThe trading volumes on the counter has surged more than eight-fold with a combined 2.93 million shares changed hands on the <a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/topic/bse\" target=\"_blank\">BSE </a>and <a class=\"storyTags\" href=\"https://www.business-standard.com/topic/nse\" target=\"_blank\">NSE </a>till 02:40 pm.</p></div>\n<br>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t\t     \t            </span><span>\n\t           \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n            </span><span>\n          </span><span>\n                  </span></div><span>\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t  </span><p>\n\t\t\t  <style>.pubDate{color:#000!important;font-size:14px!important;border-top:solid 1px #cecece;font-style:italic;font-family:'open sans';padding:10px 0 2px 0}</style>\n\t\t\t\tFirst Published: Tue, June 12 2018. 14:43 IST\t\t\t\t</p><span>\n\t  \t\t\n        </span><!-- RELATED  CONTENT --><span>\n        </span><span>\n        \n        \t \t\n        </span><!-- RELATED  CONTENT end --><span>\n\t\t\t</span><div class=\"more-stories-pagination disNone\"><span>\n\t\t\t   </span><div class=\"row-inner\"><span>\n\t\t\t      </span><div class=\"nextprev-box\"><span>\n\t\t\t         </span><div class=\"NP-title\"><span>\n\t\t\t            </span><span class=\"col-2 Tcenter\">\n\t\t\t               <p>PREVIOUS STORY</p>\n\t\t\t            </span><span>\n\t\t\t            </span><span class=\"col-2 Tcenter\">\n\t\t\t               <p>NEXT STORY</p>\n\t\t\t            </span><span>\n\t\t\t            </span><span>\n\t\t\t         </span></div><span>\n\t\t\t         </span><a class=\"btn-control-left prev\"><img src=\"https://bsmedia.business-standard.com/include/_mod/site/html5/images/icon/prev-icon.jpg\" data-pagespeed-url-hash=\"374417303\" onload=\"pagespeed.CriticalImages.checkImageForCritica